{"tid":2365261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國科興武漢肺炎疫苗：僅能提供50.38％有效防護力","createTime":"2021-01-13T14:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T15:07:16.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb6de2837aac5a93517bfa4ede16e7ea1cea60d","tid":2365261,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">中國科興武漢肺炎疫苗 CoronaVac 於巴西的第 3 階段測試數據顯示，該疫苗僅能提供 50.38% 的有效防護力（efficacy），僅略高於 50% 的世衞要求，亦遠低過此前公佈的 78%，</span>以及該疫苗在土耳其與印尼的測試結果。其餘數款由牛津大學&mdash;阿斯利康、輝瑞&mdash;BioNTech 與 Moderna 研發的西方疫苗有效防護力；則分別有 62% 、95% 與 94.1%。<br />\n<br />\nCoronaVac 是中國科興 3 款正在研發的疫苗之一，由於疫苗採用傳統滅活病毒技術，只需在 2-8 &deg;C 溫度下儲存與運送，相對輝瑞&mdash;BioNTech 與 Moderna 疫苗需在特製雪櫃的零下溫度儲存較有優勢，可在東南亞、非洲等較貧窮國家更方便地使用。<br />\n<br />\n然而，CoronaVac 在多地的臨床測試人數少，多次延誤公佈數據，完整結果也無公開，而且各地的測試標準也有差異。與其他西方疫苗的試驗方式相比，被批欠缺透明度。《立場新聞》亦整理了 CoronaVac 過去公布的資料，讓讀者在該疫苗供港前，有更多了解。<br />\n<br />\n今日相關報道：<br />\n<br />\n巴西再公佈科興疫苗數據　整體有效率僅 50.38%　剛符緊急應用要求<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3oFGDwt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3oFGDwt&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=182dac26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3oFGDwt</a><br />\n<br />\n何栢良：病毒變種或影響成效<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Kf6tsa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Kf6tsa&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=69157b4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Kf6tsa</a><br />\n<br />\n藥劑師：「好抆」如考試剛合格　籲長者接種其他疫苗<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3nHohtq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3nHohtq&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=f2478836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3nHohtq</a><br />\n<br />\n科興董事長：已向港申註冊料準時交貨<br />\n專科醫生：應交代完整數據<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3nGpqSj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3nGpqSj&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=3897426a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3nGpqSj</a><br />\n<br />\n科興疫苗保護率到底是 50.38％ 還是 78％？第 3 階段測試結果整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XBqXyd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XBqXyd&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=4104593e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XBqXyd</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ogNFCTC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogNFCTC.jpg&h=e6f98d94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42a45819d5d343473e06c9526a148a893574527e","tid":2365261,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:58:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f2feb4c06c75b4498734e6b888d092896e702cef","tid":2365261,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"36d50ab5fa96df6ee098ffb011dfee008751530f","tid":2365261,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bbeeb3d53695f3d30d587b73c270baa955740afa","tid":2365261,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:01:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"23ef6df724a711a6b83b8ff70b6402cb5c921375","tid":2365261,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"[專家請進]支那科興疫苗巴西有效率係咪只有49.6%[會全球禁賣?]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aHQuyEV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aHQuyEV</a>"}]}